{"tid":1536234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<903巴士圍捕> 我可以為前線做D乜?","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:30:08.000Z","uid":229835,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"73a05e1235f61f944c9b4fd55847d3d685b2d0b0","tid":1536234,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"假設遇見快閃前線, 作為和理非可以做D乜?<br />\n<br />\n1. 室內室外都開傘<br />\n2. 帶定套衫隨時捐出<br />\n3. 平日都載黑超黑衫, 令前線容易混入人群<br />\n4. <br />\n5. ....<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉, 相信前線, 因為佢地一直冇令香港人失望<br />\n無佢地, 我地冚家都經已全送中, <br />\n經過今次, 相信其他前線手足一定會更加審慎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>請記住, 今晚的確有地方要改善, 就一齊改善</ins></span><br />\n除左三不之外, 除左各自努力<br />\n<br />\n更要 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">配合爬, 一齊上</span></span>"},{"pid":"bdce7f8c86bb4a8a82f1f2bcf62858e47f372568","tid":1536234,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54859493ab64c17a80263189b72a19f29117749d","tid":1536234,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"檢討POST會大把<br />\n作為和理非都要檢討<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea28bb7afae286d0474930983fac76ada16a216","tid":1536234,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔知前線會做咩<br />\n但我都會配合"},{"pid":"df0be9dace050b856e81a8eb4b58366041bed793","tid":1536234,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"一個人諗唔到咁多<br />\n求指教"},{"pid":"0d3e88291cfcc31590da9825aa1a1d18d2adddde","tid":1536234,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"前線唔好灰, 我地和理非會努力架"},{"pid":"139471a95c6a060f44d731962d813aa2d563b16f","tid":1536234,"uid":307268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"一齊加油一齊要贏"},{"pid":"579df1670a357044eb2d84b442e3780d3717f59e","tid":1536234,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"累了, 但不要放棄"},{"pid":"911b1536a813caa4186813dc4f1f63690019e7ce","tid":1536234,"uid":263668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"我一向做緊3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4dd206ef88c069d7abd20918e691848a96e609b","tid":1536234,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:13:26.000Z","msg":"今晚係個教訓, 對前線如是, 對和理非都係<br />\n一齊諗諗可以點搞"},{"pid":"4c596f53cf20089f2380d3e24d9d5948e37b5ce1"